# finalecasnit

The goal of finalecasnit is to test Knapsack using four different methods and compare the speed of these four different
algorithms.

## Installation

You can install the released version of finalecasnit from [CRAN](https://CRAN.R-project.org) with:

``` r
install.packages("finalecasnit")
```
